OL,3,CBlind lawyer and boss to climb 24
OL,4,Cpeaks in 24 hours together for charity
OL,6,FMichael Smith will be tethered to his
OL,7,Fwork colleague, Jack Stacy this
OL,8,FSeptember as the pair tackle 24
OL,9,Fmountain peaks in just 24 hours to
OL,10,Fraise #150,000 for charity.
OL,12,FMichael lost his sight 15 years ago
OL,13,Fdue to a rare genetic disease called
OL,14,FLeber's hereditary optic neuropathy
OL,15,F(LHON), which causes loss of vision in
OL,16,Fthe central part of the eyes.
