OL,3,CBlind lawyer and boss to climb 24
OL,4,Cpeaks in 24 hours together for charity
OL,6,FDespite having just 10% of his vision
OL,7,Fremaining, Michael plans to summit the
OL,8,FLake District's mountains this autumn
OL,9,Fin aid of SeeAbility, the charity who
OL,10,Fhelped to "bring my hopes and dreams
OL,11,Fback" after being diagnosed with LHON
OL,12,Fsaid Michael.
OL,14,FHe will rely on his colleague Jack's
OL,15,Fguidance as the London pair attempt to
OL,16,Fclimb 24 mountains, including
OL,17,FEngland's tallest peak Scafell Pike.
