OL,3,CBlind lawyer and boss to climb 24
OL,4,Cpeaks in 24 hours together for charity
OL,6,F"In a great way, it's a metaphor
OL,7,Fshowing people in life that you've got
OL,8,Fall this great technology out there to
OL,9,Fhelp people now who can't see terribly
OL,10,Fwell, but you always need that human
OL,11,Ftouch with you," said Michael.
OL,13,F"Communication is going to be the
OL,14,Fgreatest challenge involved here, and
OL,15,Fconcentration."
