OL,3,CBlind lawyer and boss to climb 24
OL,4,Cpeaks in 24 hours together for charity
OL,6,FThe challenge will be physically
OL,7,Fdemanding and for Jack explains the
OL,8,Fhardest part is going to be looking
OL,9,Fout for both of them "telling him
OL,10,Fwhere to park his feet at every moment
OL,11,Fup and down".
OL,13,FMichael noticed his vision changing
OL,14,Fbetween 2009 and 2010 and Doctors at
OL,15,Fthe National Hospital for Neurology
OL,16,Fand Neurosurgery in London diagnosed
OL,17,Fhim with LHON telling him he would
OL,18,F"permanently lose all of the central
OL,19,Feyesight in both eyes".
