OL,3,CBlind lawyer and boss to climb 24
OL,4,Cpeaks in 24 hours together for charity
OL,6,FMichael explained how he feared he
OL,7,Fwould not "live a very fulfilling life
OL,8,Fgoing forward" but SeeAbility helped
OL,9,Fhim return to university to study and
OL,10,Ftrain to be a lawyer.
OL,12,F"When I first lost my sight, I
OL,13,Fthought, really, it was curtains,"
OL,14,Fsaid Michael.
OL,16,F"I'm not able to independently
OL,17,Fnavigate very well. I'm not able to
OL,18,Findependently read or see people's
OL,19,Ffaces, so it had a huge impact on my
OL,20,Flife," he added.
