OL,3,CBlind lawyer and boss to climb 24
OL,4,Cpeaks in 24 hours together for charity
OL,6,F"I wasn't able to pursue the career
OL,7,Fthat I set my sights on, and I went
OL,8,Fback to the drawing board, and
OL,9,Fcharities like SeeAbility were
OL,10,Finstrumental in allowing me to really
OL,11,Fgain some ambition and gain my hopes
OL,12,Fand dreams back."
