OL,3,CBlind lawyer and boss to climb 24
OL,4,Cpeaks in 24 hours together for charity
OL,6,FMichael, who has been chairman of
OL,7,FSeeAbility for one year, wanted to
OL,8,Ftake on the striking challenge to
OL,9,Fcelebrate the charity's 225th
OL,10,Fanniversary while raising money.
OL,12,FHe hopes his challenge will inspire
OL,13,Fpeople who live with sight loss and
OL,14,Fother disabilities to achieve their
OL,15,Fambitions.
OL,17,F"I want to just show, despite my lack
OL,18,Fof sight, with a bit of help from
OL,19,FJack, I can summit 24 peaks and push
OL,20,Fmy body to the limit like everyone
OL,21,Felse can," he said.
